  "brand": {
    "id": "brand_dummy",
    "displayName": "",
    "thumbnail": "data:image/png;base64,\u003d\u003d"

  "description": "This template let\u0027s you send event tracking data via an ActiveCampaign Proxy setup on Google Cloud Functions",

    "WEB"
  ]
}


___TEMPLATE_PARAMETERS___

[
  {
    "type": "TEXT",
    "name": "proxyUrl",
    "displayName": "Cloud Function Proxy URL",
    "simpleValueType": true,
    "valueValidators": [
      {
        "type": "REGEX",
        "args": [
          ".*\\.cloudfunctions\\.net\\/.*"
        ],
        "errorMessage": "This needs to be a cloudfunctions URL",
        "enablingConditions": []
      },
      {
        "type": "NON_EMPTY"
      }
    ],
    "valueHint": "e.g. https://us-central1-cloud-functions-297809.cloudfunctions.net/",
    "help": "This is the Cloud Function URL your data will be sent to to proxy your request to Active Campaign"
  },
  {
    "type": "SELECT",
    "name": "userIdMethod",
    "displayName": "User Identification Method",
    "macrosInSelect": false,
    "selectItems": [
      {
        "value": "email",
        "displayValue": "Email Address"
      },
      {
        "value": "contactId",
        "displayValue": "Contact ID"
      },
      {
        "value": "hash",
        "displayValue": "User Hash"

___SANDBOXED_JS_FOR_WEB_TEMPLATE___

// Enter your template code here.
const log = require('logToConsole');
const sendPixel = require('sendPixel');
const encodeUri = require('encodeUri');
log('data =', data);
let url;
// Call data.gtmOnSuccess when the tag is finished.
data.gtmOnSuccess();

switch(data.userIdMethod){
  case 'email':
    url = data.proxyUrl +"?action=trackEvent&eventName="+data.eventName+"&eventData="+data.eventValue+"&email="+ data.email ;
  break;
  case 'contactId':
    url = data.proxyUrl +"?action=trackEvent&eventName="+data.eventName+"&eventData="+data.eventValue+"&contactId="+ data.contactId ;
  break;
  case 'hash':
    url = data.proxyUrl +"?action=trackEvent&eventName="+data.eventName+"&eventData="+data.eventValue+"&hash="+ data.hash ;
  break;
}

log(url);
sendPixel(url, data.gtmOnSuccess(), data.gtmOnFailure());
